OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FProperty portal Zoopla has bought
OL,7,Fnewhomesforsale.co.uk as it continues
OL,8,Fto expand further into the new build
OL,9,Fmarket.
OL,11,FZoopla said the deal ` for an
OL,12,Fundisclosed amount ` will see it buy
OL,13,F100% of the new homes property site,
OL,14,Fwhich has over 200 developer
OL,15,Fcustomers, supports 2,500 active
OL,16,Fproperty developments and connects
OL,17,Fover one million buyers with
OL,18,Fproperties each year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
