OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771902191
OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FIt comes amid a concerted push by
OL,7,FZoopla to grow its new build offering,
OL,8,Fhaving recently announced tie-ups with
OL,9,Fhousebuilding giants Taylor Wimpey and
OL,10,FPersimmon Homes.
OL,12,FAs part of the efforts to further tap
OL,13,Finto this market, Zoopla has improved
OL,14,Fthe visibility of new homes on its
OL,15,Fwebsite and the consumer search
OL,16,Fexperience, promoted the benefits of
OL,17,Fnew builds and added features such as
OL,18,Fsearch by developer and affordability
OL,19,Ftools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771902191
OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FIt has also rolled out the use of
OL,7,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to help
OL,8,Flower the cost of attracting buyers,
OL,9,Fidentify "higher-intent" customers
OL,10,Fearlier and make reservation pipelines
OL,11,Fmore efficient for home builders.
OL,13,FTogether, these product innovations
OL,14,Fhave helped drive a 53% increase in
OL,15,Fthe number of new home leads for
OL,16,Fbuilders year-on-year, according to
OL,17,FZoopla.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@XO]
