OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771902191
OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FPaul Whitehead, chief executive of
OL,7,FZoopla, said the newhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,8,F(NHFS) deal was "a natural next step
OL,9,Fin our strategy".
OL,11,FHe said: "Our recent partnerships with
OL,12,FTaylor Wimpey and Persimmon
OL,13,Fdemonstrate the progress we have made
OL,14,Fand the value we deliver.
OL,16,F"The addition of newhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,17,Fwill strengthen our offer and deepen
OL,18,Four relationships with home builders
OL,19,Facross the UK."
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@PO]sD@JOUxD@AOU{D@OO]
