PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771902191
OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FAfter the deal, Stratford-upon-Avon-
OL,7,Fbased NHFS will continue as a
OL,8,Fstandalone brand and website, with its
OL,9,Fexisting leadership team, led by
OL,10,Ffounder and managing director Vernon
OL,11,FPethard.
OL,13,FAll 10 staff ` including Mr Pethard `
OL,14,Fare transferring to Zoopla following
OL,15,Fthe deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
