SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771902191
OL,3,CZoopla buys online business
OL,4,Cnewhomesforsale.co.uk
OL,6,FMark Hincks, director of
OL,7,Fnewhomesforsale.co.uk, said: "Our
OL,8,Ffocus has always been to connect
OL,9,Fdevelopers with high-intent buyers and
OL,10,Fdeliver a clear return on marketing
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,F"Joining Zoopla unlocks audience data,
OL,14,Finsights and innovation that will
OL,15,Fallow us to deliver even more value
OL,16,Ffor our customers."
OL,18,FMr Pethard founded NHFS in 1998,
OL,19,Finitially offering a range of new
OL,20,Fhomes newspapers, which later shifted
OL,21,Fonline via the website in 2009.
